name: Android 17
effect: [On Play] Add up to 1 card from your life to your hand. Then, play up to 1 <Android 18> with a cost of 3 or less from your Drop.

name: Glimpse of a Hidden Arrogance
effect: [Activate Battle] Choose your Leader or up to 1 of your Battle Cards and it gets +25000 power for the battle. Then, if you have a Battle Card with 30000 power or more, add up to 1 Battle Card with a cost of 4 or less from your Drop to your hand.

name: Zamasu : Fused
effect:
[When Attacking] If you have 7 or fewer cards in your hand, draw 1 card.
[When KO'd] Play this card from your Drop in Rest Mode. Then, you can't play <Zamasu : Fused> for the turn.

name: Son Gohan : Future
effect:
[Permanent] All of your Battle Cards with a cost of 3 can't be removed from the Battle Area by your opponent's skills.
[End of Your Turn] Choose one―
・Play up to 1 Battle Card with a cost of 3 or less from your hand.
・Choose up to 1 of your opponent's Battle Cards with a cost of 3 or less and KO it.

name: Meta-Cooler
effect:
[Blocker] (After an opponent's attack, you may switch this card to Rest Mode and change the target of the attack to this card.)
[End of Your Turn] Switch this card to Active Mode.

name: Vegeta
effect:
[When Attacking] Discard 2 cards from your hand : Until the end of your opponent's next turn, this card can't be KO'd and gets +30000 power.
[Activate Main][Once per turn] Choose up to 1 of your opponent's Battle Cards with 25000 power or less and KO it. Then, KO this card.

name: Videl
effect: [When Attacking] If you have 7 or fewer cards in your hand, add up to 1 blue non-<Videl> card with a cost of 3 or less and 《Earthling》 in its special traits from your Drop to your hand.

name: Pan : GT
effect:
[On Play] Add up to 1 card from your life to your hand.
[When Attacking](1) : Draw 1 card. Then, if you removed an energy marker for this skill, choose up to 1 of your opponent's Battle Cards with a cost of 4 or less and return it to its owner's hand.

name: Majin Buu : Evil
effect:
[On Play] Add up to 1 card from your life to your hand.
[When KO'd] Choose up to 1 of your opponent's Battle Cards and switch it to Rest Mode.

name: Son Goku : GT
effect:
[Permanent] If your Leader is <Son Goku : GT> and this card has 45000 power or more, this card gains [Double Strike].
([Double Strike] : This card inflicts 2 damage instead of 1 when attacking.)

name: A Lonesome, Final Battle
effect:
[Field] (This card remains in your Battle Area until you place another [Field].)
[Activate Battle] Switch this card to Rest Mode : Look at 2 cards from the top of your deck and place them at the top or bottom of their owner's deck in any order.
